Shanghai bank to loan 361 mln yuan to firms . The Shanghai branch of the Industrial and Commercial Bank of China has decided to lend 361 million yuan to city state - owned firms that produce famous brands , the Xinmin Evening News said on Monday . The newspaper said the loans would be used by firms in the light industrial sector to enable them to enlarge production capacity of 20 well - known products . Among the companies receiving the loans will be eight listed on Shanghai ' s stock market , including Shanghai Shangling Electric Appliances , Shanghai Hero , Shanghai Forever Bicycle and China First Pencil , the paper said . There are 58 well - known Shanghai light industrial products with a total annual turnover of 21 billion yuan , it added but gave no more details . 
